This enables HTTPS by default for the following services:
- Zend_Gdata_Books
- Zend_Gdata_Calendar
- Zend_Gdata_Docs
- Zend_Gdata_Gbase
- Zend_Gdata_Photos
- Zend_Gdata_Spreadsheets

Notably, Zend_Gdata_YouTube is omitted due to blocking issues on YouTube's end.
